&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with department leaders (Sales, Operations, HR, Supply Chain) to understand financial impacts and optimize outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct sensitivity analyses and what-if scenarios to evaluate investments, pricing, and resource allocations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify margin improvement opportunities, track KPIs, and support continuous improvement initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure accuracy of financial data, align with US GAAP and company policies, and support internal/external audits as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage ERP and BI tools (e.g., Oracle/PBCS, Power BI/Tableau) to automate reporting and enhance insights&lt;/li&gt;
