&lt;li&gt;5–7 years in FP&amp;amp;A or financial analysis roles with progressive responsibility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced Excel skills (nested formulas, Power Query, Power Pivot), detailed financial modeling (3-statement models), and proficiency with ERP/BI tools; SQL skills highly preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong presentation and communication skills with demonstrated ability to synthesize complex information and deliver clear recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A sense of urgency with strong attention to detail and high degree of accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong interpersonal skills and a demonstrated ability to lead projects, challenge assumptions, and achieve positive results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrity, accountability, and commitment to continuous improvement&lt;/li&gt;
